<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idd3b3c349-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idd3b3c34a-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">For repeal of section effective <date date="1998-10-01">Oct. 1, 1998</date>, and subsequent reenactment of section, see note set out preceding <ref href="/us/usc/t11/s1201">section 1201 of this title</ref>.</p>
