<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idd3b3c34b-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="miscellaneous" id="idd3b3c34c-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Dates</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Permanent reenactment of section effective <date date="2005-07-01">July 1, 2005</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/109/8/s1001/a/2">section 1001(a)(2) of Pub. L. 109–8</ref>, set out as a Repeal, Reenactment, and Termination of Chapter note under <ref href="/us/usc/t11/s1201">section 1201 of this title</ref>. For effective dates of section and amendments extending periods for which section was reenacted prior to permanent reenactment, see Effective Date and Effective Date of 1999, 2001, 2002, 2003, and 2004 Amendment notes set out under <ref href="/us/usc/t11/s1201">section 1201 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
